name: Frozen Stock
query:
SELECT
    tfs.sales_order as "Sales Order:Link/Sales Order:220",
	tfs.item_code as "Item Code:Link/Item:220",
	tfs.quantity as "Quantity:Float:220",
	tfs.warehouse as "Warehouse:Link/Warehouse:170",
	tfs.created_on as "Date:Date:170"
FROM
	`tabFrozen Stock` tfs
WHERE
	tfs.quantity > 0 and tfs.sales_order = %(sales_order)s
